dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.serviceneeds

Interface IDiagEventDebounceCounterBased

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDiagEventDebounceAlgorithm, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IDiagEventDebounceCounterBased
extends IEntity, IDiagEventDebounceAlgorithm
    IDiagEventDebounceCounterBased: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents the ability to indicate that the counter-based debounce algorithm shall be used by the DEM for this diagnostic monitor. This is related to set the ECUC choice container DemDebounceAlgorithmClass to DemDebounceCounterBased.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
